        "content": "<p>In <a href=\"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2504.16690\">my paper with Ye</a> we study this construction and hence we needed to give it a name. See the notion of <strong>ethereal geometric morphism</strong> (Defn 1.2.1) and then Section 1.3.</p>",
